OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Mon 16 Mar to Wed 25 Mar
OL,6,FMostly changeable through this period,
OL,7,Fwith Atlantic frontal systems passing
OL,8,Fclose to or across the UK at times.
OL,9,FThese will bring spells of rain and
OL,10,Fshowers, most frequent and heavy in
OL,11,Fthe west or northwest, and perhaps
OL,12,Faccompanied by strong winds. However,
OL,13,Fthere should also be some drier
OL,14,Finterludes under transient ridges of
OL,15,Fhigh pressure, with longer dry periods
OL,16,Fmost likely in the south and east,
OL,17,Fthough even here some wet weather is
OL,18,Fpossible at times. Temperatures will
OL,19,Fbe near average for the period as a
OL,20,Fwhole, but with some shorter-duration
OL,21,Fcolder interludes at times when frost
OL,22,Fand hill snow will be possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
